						               													<description>A dice battle platform for your favorite board game hero/miniature or anything you want.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;OVERVIEW&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Board Game Heroes is especially designed for The Game Crafter and for people who like board games and MOBA (Multiplayer-Online Battle Arena) games. This game was made similar to MOBA and also designed for board/table top gamers, especially to those who like dice battle game. Basically, this game is a platform for your favorite board game heroes/miniatures. This serves as battle arena which battles thru dice result and skill cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;OBJECTIVE&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The objective of this game is to destroy the enemy base by pushing your opponent heroes until you reach their base; Each base has 5 life points and there are 14 tiles from your starting lane up to your opponents base. Gain Mana equal to the result of your movement and draw skill card whenever you stepped on the Blue Tile, use your skill card to either advance &amp;amp; stall your enemy on same lane.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
